<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="depressed-adj">depressed <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'prest/    美 /dɪ'prest/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>忧愁的；沮丧的</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There’s no point in getting <strong>depressed about</strong> it now — it’s no use crying over spilt milk. 
现在为这事沮丧没有用——覆水难收。</p><footer>2002 上海</footer></div></div>